pullrequest.title: gz11 branch fixes to compile on Windows

content.raw: The `1: unknown file: error: SEH exception with code 0xc0000005 thrown in the test body.` errors in tests comes from the problems for finding libraries to load at runtime. The first of them refers to the lack of `ignition-common3-events.dll`in the PATH.
